{"type":null,"faqId":19332,"title":"如何截取屏幕？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>在任意界面，同时按下电源键和音量下键，可截取当前屏幕。截取的图片默认存储在</span><span class=\"s2\">图库</span><span>的“屏幕截图”文件夹内。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>下拉状态栏，点击 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64227\" style=\"width:0.22986111in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s2\">截屏</span><span>，可截取当前屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>下拉状态栏，点击 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64228\" style=\"width:0.22986111in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，长按</span><span class=\"s2\">截屏</span><span>，可截取当前屏幕任意位置。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2473","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608222000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":27,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":5,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":5.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}